             was indicted for <rs id="t18240603-227-off1178" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240603-227-off1178" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-227-off1178" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240603-227-cd1179" type="crimeDate">6th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-227-off1178 t18240603-227-cd1179"></join>, four bushels of oats, value 12 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240603-227-victim1948" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Benkinsop
                  <interp inst="t18240603-227-victim1948" type="surname" value="Benkinsop"></interp>
